  "In x = Ax + d, the matrix A contains the technical coefficients: a_ij is the amount of good i needed to produce one unit of good j. The vector d is final demand.": "",
  "For the Leontief model to have a feasible solution x = (I - A)^(-1)d, the eigenvalues of A must satisfy:": "",
